            <title>[LU-11586] sanity-pfl test_10: FAIL: /mnt/lustre/d10.sanity-pfl/file2 does not inherite root layout (subdiretory mounts)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11586</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;test_10() issue: root layout is not inherit because it is not set: test has mounted not root on MOUNT, but subdir&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
